<figure class="agent-control-loop" aria-labelledby="agent-control-loop-title agent-control-loop-caption">
  <div class="agent-control-loop__header">
    <div>
      <p class="agent-control-loop__eyebrow">CONTROL OWNERSHIP</p>
      <h3 id="agent-control-loop-title">模型提议一步，程序控制整条循环</h3>
    </div>
    <span>Proposal ≠ Execution</span>
  </div>

  <div class="agent-control-loop__shell">
    <section class="agent-control-loop__program is-start">
      <span>PROGRAM</span>
      <strong>目标与初始状态</strong>
      <small>声明成功条件、允许动作和总预算</small>
    </section>
    <b aria-hidden="true">→</b>
    <section class="agent-control-loop__program">
      <span>PROGRAM</span>
      <strong>构造 Observation</strong>
      <small>只暴露当前决策所需的公开状态</small>
    </section>
    <b aria-hidden="true">→</b>
    <section class="agent-control-loop__model">
      <span>MODEL</span>
      <strong>Action Proposal</strong>
      <small>完成、调用工具或请求澄清</small>
    </section>
    <b aria-hidden="true">→</b>
    <section class="agent-control-loop__program is-gate">
      <span>PROGRAM</span>
      <strong>策略与参数校验</strong>
      <small>拒绝越权、超预算或不合法动作</small>
    </section>
    <b aria-hidden="true">→</b>
    <section class="agent-control-loop__program">
      <span>PROGRAM</span>
      <strong>执行并验证</strong>
      <small>得到分类结果，检查真实后置条件</small>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="agent-control-loop__outcomes" aria-label="循环结果">
    <section class="is-complete">
      <span>COMPLETE</span>
      <strong>成功条件成立</strong>
      <small>提交输出和可验证证据</small>
    </section>
    <section class="is-loop">
      <span>CONTINUE</span>
      <strong>状态发生有效变化</strong>
      <small>扣减预算后返回下一轮 Observation</small>
    </section>
    <section class="is-stop">
      <span>STOP</span>
      <strong>拒绝、取消或人工接管</strong>
      <small>保留停止原因，不让模型覆盖程序边界</small>
    </section>
  </div>

  <figcaption id="agent-control-loop-caption">
    Agent 的“不确定性”只存在于候选动作选择。程序仍拥有循环入口、可执行动作集合、预算、验证器、状态提交和所有终止路径。
  </figcaption>
</figure>

